urce/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ramos' final chances of reaching the Olympics hinged on the decision of Belgium's Nina Sterckx, who needed to choose which division she wanted to compete in as she qualified for both the women's 49kg and 59kg divisions.\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"score\": 0.9999999326767033, \"rank\": 5.666217179125785e-08, \"text\": \"Ramos\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fidel_V._Ramos\"}, {\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7439755244226476, \"rank\": 0.34010117546283414, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1145, \"end\": 1149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\", \"score\": 0.999999915514767, \"rank\": 8.447847547655339e-08, \"text\": \"Nina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nina_Girado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sterckx produced best lifts of 193kg in the women's 49kg and 220kg in the women's 59kg for a double qualification.\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1398, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But according to national coach Toni Agustin, Sterckxpicked the women's 49kg category, dashing Ramos' hopes of joiningElreen Ando(women's 59kg),Vanessa Sarno(women's 71kg), andJohn Ceniza(men's 61kg) in Paris.\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpe